data.title: Very good!
data.text: Being San Diegans I admit that we're taco shop snobs. But I have to say we were very satisfied with the selection of foods and the quality of our order. I was especially pleased with the salsa bar. Lots of good options there you don't always see. Next time we are in town we'll have to try the various fish dishes, which seemed to be their specialty. Being our first time there we stuck to the basics.
